original_title: Les Mills Combat - Warrior 2: Lower Body Lean Out
overview: Rach leads the workout in what is really another cardio routine with a martial arts flavor.  That means kicks, squats and some plyo…but mainly kicks.  That means if you ever find yourself in a bar surrounded by ninjas, you’ll be good as gold so long as a funky beat is playing on the speakers.
title: Les Mills Combat - Warrior 2: Lower Body Lean Out
